| Concurrent transfer with overdraft | Exactly one succeeds, others fail with insufficient funds |
| Two concurrent transfers from same account | Serialized, no overdraft |
| System crash mid-transaction | Rollback ensures atomicity |
| SERIALIZABLE vs REPEATABLE READ comparison | Verify phantom read prevention under load |
| Deadlock detection | Verify retry mechanism activates |
| Idempotency | Duplicate requests handled safely |

