-- Check balance, then update if sufficient
UPDATE Accounts SET balance = balance - 60 WHERE account_id = 1;
COMMIT;
```

## Anomaly Prevention

Use atomic UPDATE statements with balance checks to ensure sufficient funds exist before withdrawal, or implement explicit row locking with SELECT FOR UPDATE to serialize access at the application level.
